I awoke suddenly to the sound of wet skin slapping against wet skin, the sound of metal shearing, and the low drawn out cries of agony and ecstasy. Slowly I turned my head towards the direction that the sound was emanating from. And there I saw what can only be described as the most horrific and gruesome sight to ever have eyes laid upon. So horrid and disgusting that it cannot even be mentioned. As I lay there in shear terror at this spectacle, I could only think of one single thing…

That’s kinda… disturbing, sorry.

Setting Jane on the floor of the primary chamber, I undressed her, then lifted her onto the chair. Her ass settled on two flat bars, leaving her entire crotch accessible. Legs stretched out in a dramatic V, parallel with the floor, while her arms strapped behind her at wrist and elbow, then attached to an upright bar. @error.login wrote:

I was just waking up, the sound of my father having sex with another guy. Just an average day for me, just like yesterday, and the day before that. Today I was going to present my report on gay pride. School is in 1 hour Dad moaned to me. I had finished my report the night before, rushing through it so i could watch X-Factor. I was in for a surprise, my school was closed. In fact, everything was closed, and the whole town was empty. Even moparisthebest.com was closed down. I was alone, I thought it was a dream, so I tried fisting myself and failed. I realized that this was in fact, real life. and that everyone just watched me try and fist myself. I felt violated, and insecure.

I think this is a lot better
